{"search_data": "MaharashtraPandit Deen Dayal Upadhyay Krishi Margdarshak YojanaUnder the scheme, the government will update the farmers with the knowledge of new discoveries, inventions and suitable guidance in agriculture sector. This will be done via a single platform which will be framed under the Deen Dayal Upadhyay Krishi Margdarshan Yojana.The government has proposed an outlay of Rs. 60 Crore for the new scheme in the 2016-17 budget.Other than this scheme, the state government has also announced few other schemes for the betterment of the agriculture sector. Two of those schemes are Palakmantri Panand Raste Yojana and Palakmantri Earth Moving Machine Kharedi Yojana.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now  at  "}